[A-pril] /eIpr3l/ (SAMPA) - also in '''de''' /april/, '''nl''' [a-pril] /aprIl/

#April is the fourth [[month]] in the Gregorian [[calendar]]. It has 30 [[day]]s.

==Etymology==
From Latin [[aprilis]]. First in 1297 as ''aueril'', later re-latinized to ''apprile''.

